content.no: Fikk nettopp denne saken i hus 🤩 [Suzuki Omnichord OM-84](equipment/instruments/suzuki-omnichord-om-84-system-two/) 🎛️ Tusen takk til Charlie på Riffers for fantastisk service 👍 UPS klarte å ødelegge den første i frakt, selv om den var forsvarlig pakket, men Charlie fikk tak i en ny 😃
content.en: Just got this beauty 🤩 [Suzuki Omnichord OM-84](equipment/instruments/suzuki-omnichord-om-84-system-two/) 🎛️ Thanks a lot to Charlie at Riffers for amazing service 👍 UPS managed to break the first one in transit, even though it was securely packed, but Charlie got me a new one 😃

content.en: Got this beautiful Wurlitzer neon sign from Ruth 66 today 😃 The photos doesn't really do it justice. It looks a lot more vibrant in person 🤩
